# pnpm 11 refuses to expand env vars in project .npmrc (the file
# is committed and could leak the secret to an attacker-controlled
# registry). The cluj adapter only needs the @n3ary/gtfs-spec dep
# (and a public dep scope for any future ones), so the .npmrc is
# just the scope mapping. The auth token is written to user-level
# ~/.npmrc at install time by the CI workflow, mirroring the app
# repo's pattern.
@n3ary:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
